The paper discusses the use of mobile robots for autonomous exploration, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the use of reinforcement learning for implementing learning in robots, which falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also describes a multiagent approach for implementing reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of multiagent systems (cs.MA). Finally, the paper discusses the use of a behavior-based architecture, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY).
